device=`adb devices|grep -v "List of devices"|awk 'NF==2{print $1}'|awk 'BEGIN{all=""} {all =$0"\n"all} END{if(NR==1) {print($0)} else{system("echo \""all "\"|peco") } }'`
echo "use" $device
target=`adb -s $device shell pm list package|sed -e 's/^package://g'|peco`
adb -s $device shell << EOS
run-as $target
cd shared_prefs
grep -n "" *
exit
exit
EOS
